title: ► American Horror Story 6: Teeth
author: American Horror Story 10
comment: this was the real teaser for season 6

Only one of the teasers is real, and I believe it is this one! I think Gaga is going to be an evil, disgusting 'tooth fairy'. And the central theme will be based around Native American Indians and a tribe in the past.
description:
American Horror Story: Season 6. Trailer / Promo FX Television Network. 2016.
American Horror Story: Season 6 premieres Sept. 14th on FX and features Sarah Paulson, Matt Bomer, Lady Gaga, Finn Wittrock, Angela Bassett, Kathy Bates, Evan Peters, Denis O’Hare and Cheyenne Jackson.
